  "prompt": "What does \u597d\u840c\u963f mean?",
  "response": "\u597d\u840c\u554a (h\u01ceo m\u00e9ng \u0101) is a phrase in Chinese that can be translated to \"so cute!\" or \"so adorable!\" in English. This expression is typically used to describe something or someone that is very cute and endearing. \"\u597d\" (h\u01ceo) means \"very\" or \"so,\" \"\u840c\" (m\u00e9ng) means \"cute\" or \"adorable,\" and \"\u554a\" (\u0101) is an exclamation particle used to emphasize the sentiment.",
